# CI sibling-checkout scaffolding (Phase V.A.2): GitHub Actions
# workflows checkout sibling repos into _deps/<name>/. These are
# build-time artifacts, never committed. Keeps 'git status' clean
# if a developer mirrors CI locally via 'gh workflow run' or the
# equivalent manual checkout. Added by Phase V.A.0 audit (Agent 2 #1).
_deps/
